description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'Gentle Seated Yoga For Beginners & All Levels | 30 Minute Practice' from the channel Jess Yoga.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a slow and gentle 30-minute yoga practice of seated and floor stretches, perfect for every body, suitable for beginners and all levels. 
Take this time for yourself to move and stretch your entire body. Be present as you connect with your breath, watch your thoughts and observe the sensations that arise. After this yoga class, you will feel relaxed and rejuvenated.

If you enjoyed this video, check out a few other beginner friendly classes:
https://bit.ly/2QTaC4R
